Class DeclutterableText

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.worldwind.render.DeclutterableText
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Declutterable, OrderedRenderable, Renderable

    public class DeclutterableText
extends java.lang.Object
implements Declutterable
    A wrapper around GeographicText that allows provides participation in global text decluttering.
